Ghanatɔwo ƒe mɔzɔzɔ yi Germany dzegɔme le ƒe 1950 lɔƒo esime yetoɖoƒe Germany ƒe nuŋɔŋlɔ ɖe mɔ na sukuviwo tso Afrika dukɔ aɖewo me be na woateŋu akpɔ gome le sukukɔkɔ dede me.  Agbale sia ɖe mɔ be na sukuviawo na srɔ nu eye ne wo trɔ gbɔ va woƒe dukɔ vovovoawo me la, any kpekpeɖeŋu.

Va de asi ne ƒe 2009, xexleme abe 40,000 lɔƒo nye "Ghanavidzidziwo ƒe mɔzɔzɔƒe dzɔtsoƒe nye Ghana" le Germany; esime "Ghanavidzidziwo ƒe mɔzɔzɔƒe dzɔtsoƒe nye Ghana" gɔmee nye  "amesiwo dzi alo ƒe dzotsoƒee nye Ghana" eye " dzidzime evelia kple dzidzime etɔlia siwo dzɔ tso Ghanavi dzidziwo me si wo le Germany eye devisiwo dzɔ tso dukɔ eve ƒe kadodo me siwo me zɔ mɔ le woɖokuisiwo o, abe alesi Deutsche Gesellschaft fur Technische Zusammenarbeit (GTZ) ŋlɔe ene.

Le GTZ ƒe nuŋɔŋlɔ me la, ame agbɔ sɔsɔ geɖe wo nye mɔzɔla siwo le Germany mɔzɔgbale deditɔ manɔ si o. Wo ame sia wo zɔ mɔ kple agbale deditɔwo gake wo me gbugbɔ yi woƒe tsoƒewo o, ke boŋ le Germany le esime wo me ŋlɔ ŋkɔ be yewo anɔ anyi awu ŋkeke si so na wo la o.

== Nusiwo hea mɔzɔzɔ va nɛ ==
Ga manɔ ame si, aua wɔwɔ kple agbeme kuzɛwoe nye susu siwo tae amewo uu na le woƒe dukɔ si wo dzɔtso la me.  Ame siwo shi tso awawɔwɔ alo hunyahunya he le sitsoƒe sim la ƒe agbosɔsɔme le xexeame le dzika ɖem ƒo eye wo le dzi yim ƒe sia ƒe. Ga manɔ amesi, kododo ƒe dziyiyi kple dukɔmeviwo ƒe agbɔsɔsɔ ƒe dziyiyi woe nye susu aɖe siwo tae amewo Uu na le woƒe duwo me. 

== Mɔzɔzɔ tso Ghana yi Germany ƒe hatsotsowo ==
Ne mie le ŋku de Ghanaviwo ƒe mɔzɔzɔ yi ɖe Germany me la, mia kpɔ hatsotso etɔ. Woa we nye sukudede mɔzɔzɔ, sisoƒe-didi mɔzɔzɔ, kple ƒome wo ƒe gododo mɔzɔzɔ. Dɔwɔwɔ mɔzɔ gbale xɔxɔ ƒe dzidzedze me sɔ ne Ghanaviwo o.  

=== Sukudede mɔzɔzɔ ===
Ame geɖe siwo zɔmɔ yi Germany be ye wo aɖe suku la, trɔ gbɔna va woƒe tsoƒewo.

=== Sisoƒe-didi mɔzɔzɔ ===
Ame siwo zɔme le xexi ya te lae nye amesiwo le Germany egbe eye wo anɔe daa.

Tso ƒe 1970 la, ga manɔ amesi kple dunya ta UliUli ƒe hunyahunya wo le gbadagba wo ƒe kpɔkplɔ te le Ghana nae be Ghana vi gedewo di sitsoƒe le Yurope kple Afrika dukɔwo me. 

Xɔxɔna amesiwo di sitsoƒe tso Ghana kuda dunya UiUli hunyahunya ta la ƒe xexleme me ɖo ɖeka ɖe alafa ɖeka dzi o, elabena dunyataUlila geɖewo tsɔna wo dea Ga ma nɔ amesi sitsoƒe sila wo dome.  Ame 112 tso ƒe 1983 va se ɖe 2007 koe wo xɔ abe dunya ta UliUli ƒe hunyahunya sitoƒe silawo ene.

=== Ƒome wo ƒe gododo mɔzɔzɔ ===
Ame siwo zɔme le xexi ya te lae nye amesiwo le Germany egbe eye wo anɔe daa. Ghanaviwo siwo wu ɖeka ɖe akpa ene dzi woe zɔmɔ yi Getmany to ƒome gododo me.
